Like Kim Clement said, 'You tried to put a witch in the White House, but we blocked it.'Trump will be a trumpet.

00:42:48.346 --> 00:43:12.509
This is the time we've all been waiting for. This will be an America that prays again.

00:43:12.510 --> 00:43:35.943
